data.title: Tyson Chandler 2008-09 Upper Deck #132 New Orleans Hornets
data.meta_description:
This trading card features Tyson Chandler of the New Orleans Hornets during the 2008-09 season. The card is part of the 2008-09 Upper Deck set and has the card number #132. The card is a single product and is perfect for collectors who are fans of the National Basketball Association (NBA).

The card is not autographed and is not graded, but it is in great condition and is perfect for any fan of Tyson Chandler or the New Orleans Hornets. The card is a modern card manufactured by Upper Deck, one of the leading manufacturers of sports trading cards. Add this card to your collection today!
